orts ministry\", \"from\": 7212, \"to\": 7239}, {\"ngram\": \"the Gymnastics Federation\", \"from\": 7253, \"to\": 7278}, {\"ngram\": \"India\", \"from\": 7282, \"to\": 7287}, {\"ngram\": \"its nine qualified athletes\", \"from\": 7305, \"to\": 7332}, {\"ngram\": \"the selection criteria\", \"from\": 7337, \"to\": 7359}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 7364, \"to\": 7373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were sent the criteria for qualification after seven or eight days of the trials,\\\" the gymnast says.\", \"from\": 7376, \"to\": 7480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the criteria\", \"from\": 7390, \"to\": 7402}, {\"ngram\": \"qualification\", \"from\": 7407, \"to\": 7420}, {\"ngram\": \"seven or eight days\", \"from\": 7427, \"to\": 7446}, {\"ngram\": \"the trials\", \"from\": 7450, \"to\": 7460}, {\"ngram\": \"the gymnast\", \"from\": 7463, \"to\": 7474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If the administration had been more proactive, I would have received the criteria ahead of the trials, not a week after.\\\"\", \"from\": 7481, \"to\": 7603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the administration\", \"from\": 7485, \"to\": 7503}, {\"ngram\": \"the criteria\", \"from\": 7551, \"to\": 7563}, {\"ngram\": \"the trials\", \"from\": 7573, \"to\": 7583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Paris Games, Phogat's dramatic exit has shone a spotlight on what critics have decried as the lack of support from sports administrators who were supposed to look out for her.\", \"from\": 7605, \"to\": 7787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7625, \"end\": 7631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 7608, \"to\": 7623}, {\"ngram\": \"a spotlight\", \"from\": 7658, \"to\": 7669}, {\"ngram\": \"critics\", \"from\": 7678, \"to\": 7685}, {\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 7702, \"to\": 7710}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 7714, \"to\": 7721}, {\"ngram\": \"sports administrators\", \"from\": 7727, \"to\": 7748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Phogat was guaranteed to win at least a silver medal, and had a good chance at gold, before she was disqualified on the morning of the final for coming in overweight - by as little as 100 grams, according to some reports.\", \"from\": 7789, \"to\": 8010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Phogat\", \"from\": 7789, \"to\": 7795}, {\"ngram\": \"at least a silver medal\", \"from\": 7818, \"to\": 7841}, {\"ngram\": \"a good chance\", \"from\": 7851, \"to\": 7864}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 7868, \"to\": 7872}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 7905, \"to\": 7916}, {\"ngram\": \"overweight\", \"from\": 7944, \"to\": 7954}, {\"ngram\": \"as little as 100 grams\", \"from\": 7960, \"to\": 7982}, {\"ngram\": \"some reports\", \"from\": 7997, \"to\": 8009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Officials said she tried to cut weight through the night before the final, cycling and running, but to no avail.\", \"from\": 8011, \"to\": 8123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Officials\", \"from\": 8011, \"to\": 8020}, {\"ngram\": \"weight\", \"from\": 8043, \"to\": 8049}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 8058, \"to\": 8067}, {\"ngram\": \"the final, cycling\", \"from\": 8075, \"to\": 8093}, {\"ngram\": \"no avail\", \"from\": 8114, \"to\": 8122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am surprised and I feel very bad for the athlete,\\\" says Subbaiah.\", \"from\": 8125, \"to\": 8193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 8165, \"to\": 8176}, {\"ngram\": \"Subbaiah\", \"from\": 8184, \"to\": 8192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am also surprised that she was training the whole night.\", \"from\": 8194, \"to\": 8253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Without ea